      Creates an Appointments object with all of the required fields
      Parameters:
      apptId - Unique appointment ID
      apptTitle - Appointment title
      apptDesc - Description of appointment (optional)
      apptLocation - Appointment location
      apptContact - Appointment contact
      apptContactId - Contact ID associated with contact
      apptType - Type of appointment
      apptStart - Start time for appointment
      apptEnd - End time for appointment
      apptCustomerId - Contact relation to customer ID
      apptUserId - User ID associated with appointment
